Tema 1:

- register
- algoritm/metoda pentru a lua categoriile sub forma unui tree
- de terminat toate metodele din category controller (getAll, update, get, delete)

Tema 2:

- users must verify email on register
- forgot password
- openapi swagger update documentation
- de terminat toate metodele din product controller (add, update, get, delete)



Comenzi utile:

php artisan storage:link  -> generate symlink for storage files
php artisan migrate:fresh --seed   -> recreate tables and seed data
composer install   -> install vendor dependencies
php artisan make:model Product --migration   -> create a new model and associated migration
php artisan make:controller   -> create new controller
php artisan     -> see list of all available commands
